Sentencas: Nanocrystalline Yb-doped scandia-stabilized zirconia (6Yb4ScSZ) powders are prepared using co-precipitation process.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: The effects of calcination treatments on factors such as phase evolution, crystallite size, and specific surface area are investigated.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: The synthesized electrolyte powders have a high specific area of 25m(2) g(-1), nanocrystalline size of 17nm and ionic conductivity of 0.7 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C with a cubic structure.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with anode-supported electrolyte, in which the electrolyte layer consists of nanocrystalline 6Yb4ScSZ powders calcined at 850 degrees C, is fabricated by tape casting and co-sintering.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: The open-circuit voltage of the SOFC single cell is approximately 1.07V at 800 degrees C, indicating negligible leakage of fuel through the electrolyte layer.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering

Sentencas: As a result, power density of 1.30Wcm(-2) is obtained at 2.0Acm(-2) and 800 degrees C due to the drastic reduction of ohmic resistance in the SOFC cell.
Titulo: Fabrication and electrochemical characterization of SOFC single cell with 6Yb4ScSZ electrolyte powder by tape-casting and co-sintering
